# {{rfv-sense}} A defensive [[entrenchment]] consisting of a [[trench]] and [[parapet]].
# A [[reduction]] or [[curtailment]]; often referring to a business or government agency cutting back operations or laying off workers.
# {{military|dated}} A defensive work constructed within another, to prolong the defense of the position when the enemy has gained possession of the outer work; or to protect the defenders till they can retreat or obtain terms for a capitulation.

